New Johannesburg Mayor Mpho Moerane. JOHANNESBURG - Former Joburg mayor Mpho Moerane is in a stable condition and reportedly in good spirits. The ANC caucus leader was involved in a car accident late on Monday night. READ: Moerane in critical condition after car crash A statement from his family said that Moerane is responding well to treatment. The family has appealed to the public not to speculate about his condition and to continue praying for a speedy recovery. 